column2: SELECT   p.objID, p.ra, p.dec, dbo.fPhotoTypeN(p.type) as type FROM #upload u  JOIN #x x ON x.up_id = u.up_id  JOIN PhotoTag p ON p.objID = x.objID WHERE ((p.flags & dbo.fPhotoFlags(SATURATED)) != #) OR ((p.psfMag_r - p.modelMag_r) < # AND p.psfMag_r < # AND p.clean = # AND p.probPSF = #)
